 product officer of global electronic product development organization for lexisnexis since october  he was responsible for the development of nextgeneration products for lexisnexis including the development of online products using a global approach prior to  he served as senior vice president of product development at celera genomics after joining celera in  he led construction of a new online system containing information about human genetics deployed in taskbased applications for research scientists delivered via the internet he served at lexisnexis as an engineer and then manager and director in building data and operating editorial systems in  he joined lexis online publishing to head product design he served as vicepresident of product development of lexis online where he led the teams that designed and built all the components of the lexiscomò research system including core terms search advisor core concepts case law summaries and legislative linking he headed creation of a new editorial publishing system for the summaries and launched the summaries operations he serves as the chairman of visionary systems inc and diversified data development corp he serves as a director at transunion rental screening solutions inc and transunion corp he serves as a director of lexisnexis special services inc he serves as a director of transunion he served as a director of choicepoint inc mr peck has bachelors degree from the university of dayton in management information systems and a masters in business administration from ohio state universityread full background corporate headquarters  west adams streetchicago illinois united statesphone fax  board members memberships directortransunion rental screening solutions incchief executive officer president and directortransunion intermediate holdings incchairmanvisionary systems incdirectorlexisnexis special services incchairmandiversified data development corpchairman chief executive officer and presidenttransunion financing c